# Day 4 – Project 5: Write Your Own Scene (COMPLETED EXAMPLE)
# Teacher reference — shows what a finished student template might look like.
# =============================================================================

define maya = Character("Maya")
define dr_chen = Character("Dr. Chen")


label start:

    "The robotics lab was empty at 7 AM — or so Maya thought."

    "She pushed open the door and froze."

    "Someone was already there, hunched over a workbench in the corner."

    dr_chen "You're here early."

    maya "I could say the same thing. The competition is in three days."

    dr_chen "Two days and fourteen hours, to be precise."

    "Dr. Chen turned around. She was holding a circuit board the size of a dinner plate."

    maya "Is that... the new navigation module?"

    dr_chen "What's left of it."

    "Maya felt her stomach drop."

    maya "What happened?"

    dr_chen "That's what I'm trying to figure out. Get your toolkit."

    "Maya set down her bag."

    "This was going to be a long morning."

    return
